    "body": "Problem: No public method for treesitter incremental selection\r\n\r\nSolution: Add a method `vim.treesitter.select()`\r\n\r\nCloses: #38211\r\n",
    "closed_at": null,
    "comment_data": [],
    "comment_regular_data": [
        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Would it be prohibitively difficult for this to return info about the selection and/or info about the selected node? This would make it possible to take the selection and build functionality on top of it.\r\n\r\nUse case: Plugins like treeclimber or flash, which show sibling node info on selection.",
